A vast, intricate network of glowing crystalline nodes floating in deep space, each node containing miniature architectural blueprints and organizational flowcharts rendered as delicate origami-like paper structures. The nodes connect through luminous threads of cyan and gold light, forming a three-dimensional web that suggests hierarchy and purpose. In the foreground, a large translucent prism refracts the connections into rainbow spectrums, while smaller geometric shapes orbit slowly around major junction points. The scene has a cyberpunk aesthetic with neon accents against the void of space, circuit-board patterns subtly etched into the crystal surfaces, and holographic data streams flowing between structures like digital rivers. The overall composition suggests order emerging from complexity, strategy made visible and interconnected.
